headline: Has Cencora’s 55.9% 2025 Rally Outpaced Its Fundamental Value?
summary: If you are wondering whether Cencora's hot run still leaves room for value, you are not alone. That is exactly what we are going to unpack here. The stock has climbed 55.9% year to date and 53.6% over the last year, even after a recent 3.2% dip over the past month. This suggests the market is still recalibrating its view on the shares. Much of the recent interest in Cencora has been tied to its evolving role in the healthcare supply chain and strategic moves to strengthen its specialty...

headline: Cencora takes majority stake in cancer care platform OneOncology for $5B
summary: The drug distributor has been steadily building up its specialty support assets as it looks to increase access to drugs.
